                    <note>One miracle of Mary</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="100v" to="101v" facs="103"/>
                    <title>The Spiritual Benefit of Prayer and Reading Scripture</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡  <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ ዘይትገበር፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን። ፩ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ፍሬሁ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="102r" facs="104"> f. 102r, lower</locus>
                    <title>Gǝ‘ǝz poem</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ገሞራ፡ ወሰዶም፡ ወይጣልያ፡ ዋህደ፡ ኮኑ፡ በምግባሮሙ፡</incipit>
                    <note>excerpt of Gǝ‘ǝz poem</note>
                  </msItem>
